<li class="next-article"><div class="next-article-header"><h1>Next in Leaders</h1><span class="close_carousel" data-ec-omniture="ux|nextprev|closebutton">X</span></div><div><a data-ec-omniture="ux|nextprev|article" href="/news/leaders/21588093-latin-america-must-press-nicol-s-maduro-not-use-decree-powers-throttle-his-opposition" class="next-article-body"><div class="next-article-content"><h2>Venezuela’s president</h2><h3>The crunch in Caracas</h3><p class="article-next-rubric">Latin America must press Nicolás Maduro not to use decree powers to throttle his opposition</p></div></a></div></li>
